skills/skill-versioning.content:
Versionado
Skills se versionan por directorio.
Estructura
.skills/
└── skills/
    └── testing/
        ├── manifest.json
        └── versions/
            ├── v1.0.0/
            │   └── SKILL.md
            └── v1.1.0/
                └── SKILL.md

manifest.json
{
  &quot;name&quot;: &quot;testing&quot;,
  &quot;description&quot;: &quot;Testing patterns&quot;,
  &quot;versions&quot;: {
    &quot;v1.0.0&quot;: {
      &quot;created&quot;: &quot;2025-01-15&quot;,
      &quot;platforms&quot;: [&quot;linux&quot;, &quot;windows&quot;]
    },
    &quot;v1.1.0&quot;: {
      &quot;created&quot;: &quot;2025-02-20&quot;,
      &quot;platforms&quot;: [&quot;linux&quot;]
    }
  }
}
Forks
Versiones específicas por plataforma son forks:
versions/
├── v1.0.0/          # Versión base
├── v1.1.0/          # Base actualizada
└── v1.1.0-windows/  # Fork de Windows

Manifest de fork:
{
  &quot;forked_from&quot;: &quot;v1.1.0&quot;,
  &quot;platform&quot;: &quot;windows&quot;
}
Índice global
version.json en raíz del skill:
{
  &quot;version&quot;: &quot;1.2.0&quot;,
  &quot;skills&quot;: {
    &quot;testing&quot;: {
      &quot;latest&quot;: &quot;v1.1.0&quot;,
      &quot;platforms&quot;: [&quot;linux&quot;]
    }
  }
}
